024/**
025 * information for Examples object.
026 *
027 * <p>
028 * The Example Object provides an example of a media type. The example object is mutually exclusive of the examples 
029 * object. Furthermore, if referencing a schema which contains an example, the example value shall override the example 
030 * provided by the schema.
031 *
032 * <h5 class='section'>OpenAPI Specification:</h5>
033 * <p>
034 * The Example Object is composed of the following fields:
035 * <ul class='spaced-list'>
036 *    <li><c>summary</c> (string) - Short description for the example
037 *    <li><c>description</c> (string) - Long description for the example. CommonMark syntax MAY be used for rich text representation
038 *    <li><c>value</c> (any) - Embedded literal example. The value field and externalValue field are mutually exclusive
039 *    <li><c>externalValue</c> (string) - A URI that points to the literal example. This provides the capability to reference 
040 *       examples that cannot easily be included in JSON or YAML documents. The value field and externalValue field are mutually exclusive
041 * </ul>
042 *
043 * <h5 class='section'>Example:</h5>
044 * <p class='bcode'>
045 *    <jc>// Construct using SwaggerBuilder.</jc>
046 *    Example <jv>x</jv> = <jsm>example</jsm>()
047 *       .setSummary(<js>"User example"</js>)
048 *       .setValue(<js>"John Doe"</js>);
049 *
050 *    <jc>// Serialize using JsonSerializer.</jc>
051 *    String <jv>json</jv> = Json.<jsm>from</jsm>(<jv>x</jv>);
052 *
053 *    <jc>// Or just use toString() which does the same as above.</jc>
054 *    <jv>json</jv> = <jv>x</jv>.toString();
055 * </p>
056 * <p class='bcode'>
057 *    <jc>// Output</jc>
058 *    {
059 *       <js>"summary"</js>: <js>"User example"</js>,
060 *       <js>"value"</js>: <js>"John Doe"</js>
061 *    }
062 * </p>
063 *
064 * <h5 class='section'>See Also:</h5><ul>
065 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="https://spec.openapis.org/oas/v3.0.0#example-object">OpenAPI Specification &gt; Example Object</a>
066 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="https://swagger.io/docs/specification/adding-examples/">OpenAPI Adding Examples</a>
067 *    <li class='link'><a class="doclink" href="https://juneau.apache.org/docs/topics/JuneauBeanOpenApi3">juneau-bean-openapi-v3</a>
068 * </ul>
069 */
